Resource Profile: CH Core Composition EPR

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-core/StructureDefinition/ch-core-composition-epr Version: 5.0.0
Active as of 2024-12-17 Computable Name: CHCoreCompositionEPR

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

Definition of the Composition resource for use in the context of the electronic patient record (EPR).

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: CH Core Document EPR
  • Refer to this Resource Profile: CH Core Composition EPR
  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Composition/ZuweisungZurRadiologischenDiagnostik

IdGradePath(s)DetailsRequirements

: contained.contained.empty()
